headline: Las Vegas’ Rio Hotel & Casino joins Destination by Hyatt
summary: Following the first phase of a $340 million renovation, the luxury resort — in a “vibrant” location for leisure, convention and group travel — has transitioned under Hyatt’s Independent Collection.
